.START 

Julius L. Marcus was named to the newly created post of senior vice president and assistant group executive of this business-machines maker.
He will assume direct responsibility for the company's printing-systems development organization.
Mr. Marcus has been president and chief executive officer of Genigraphics Corp., Syracuse, N.Y. Separately, Leonard Vickers was named senior vice president of marketing, also a newly created position.
He had operated his own New York marketing consulting firm. 

